---
// src/components/index/Testimonial.astro
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-500 mb-3 font-medium">Testimonials</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">What Parishes Say</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-warm-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-warm-200">
        <div class="text-brand-300 mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-brand-800/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">"Our website finally feels like it belongs to our parish. The daily readings bring people back every morning. It's been wonderful."</p>
        <div>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm">Fr. Michael O'Connor</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-brand-800/40">St. Mary's Parish, Dublin</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-warm-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-warm-200">
        <div class="text-brand-300 mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-brand-800/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">"The livestream integration was seamless. Our elderly parishioners can now follow Mass from home. Churchify made the whole process painless."</p>
        <div>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm">Sr. Catherine Ryan</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-brand-800/40">Holy Trinity Parish, Cork</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-warm-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-warm-200">
        <div class="text-brand-300 mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-brand-800/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">"We went from having no website to a professional online presence in weeks. The notices system is exactly what we needed. Brilliant value."</p>
        <div>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-sm">John Murphy</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-brand-800/40">Parish Secretary, St. James, Galway</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
